            "value": "Tips 🐾"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tips: borsta tänderna eller ge tuggben – tandhälsa påverkar hela hunden.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tip: brush the teeth or give a chew – dental health affects the whole dog."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tips: färskt vatten alltid framme – särskilt varma dagar.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tip: always keep fresh water out – especially on warm days."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tips: kolla tassarna efter promenaden, särskilt mellan trampdynorna.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tip: check the paws after the walk, especially between the pads."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tips: korta träningspass flera gånger om dagen slår ett långt.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tip: several short training sessions a day beat one long one."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tips: låt hunden nosa klart ibland, det är mental motion.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tip: let your dog finish sniffing sometimes – it's mental exercise."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tips: variera promenadrutten – nya dofter tröttar hjärnan mer än extra minuter.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tip: vary your walking route – new scents tire the brain more than extra minutes."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tips: väg din hund regelbundet, små förändringar syns tidigast på vågen.": {
